♪I can only sigh in my heart♪

116
00:07:56,140 --> 00:07:57,550
You're everything

117
00:07:57,550 --> 00:07:58,740
to me now.

118
00:07:58,740 --> 00:08:02,430
♪The sighs of dust rise with the wind♪

119
00:08:02,440 --> 00:08:03,280
Ruoruo.

120
00:08:04,880 --> 00:08:05,720
Ruoruo?

121
00:08:09,110 --> 00:08:10,850
What are you thinking about?

122
00:08:12,800 --> 00:08:13,890
Why are you here?

123
00:08:15,800 --> 00:08:18,070
I finally found the caravans

124
00:08:18,070 --> 00:08:20,770
you asked for,

125
00:08:21,190 --> 00:08:22,110
after a lot of effort.

126
00:08:22,110 --> 00:08:23,010
Really?

127
00:08:28,030 --> 00:08:28,880
Here

128
00:08:28,880 --> 00:08:30,320
is the secret base of the caravans.

129
00:08:45,520 --> 00:08:49,770
Wolfberry pollen,
black spiderwort, and red snake beans.

130
00:08:51,720 --> 00:08:53,160
It really is here.

131
00:08:53,560 --> 00:08:55,520
I took on the mission myself.

132
00:08:55,520 --> 00:08:56,890
How could I be wrong?

133
00:08:57,640 --> 00:08:58,600
But,

134
00:08:58,600 --> 00:09:02,200
you would never guess
who the real owner of this pharmacy is.

135
00:09:03,960 --> 00:09:05,200
If it's not Xiao Nanyang,

136
00:09:05,310 --> 00:09:06,520
then it must be Lin Yuexi.

137
00:09:10,560 --> 00:09:12,520
As expected, you're so clever.

138
00:09:12,720 --> 00:09:13,730
It's them.

139
00:09:14,640 --> 00:09:15,850
That's great.

140
00:09:16,720 --> 00:09:18,770
With this evidence,

141
00:09:19,840 --> 00:09:22,850
we can finally bring them to justice.

142
00:09:29,720 --> 00:09:32,650
The plague we created in Jiangzhou
has fully erupted.

143
00:09:33,600 --> 00:09:34,560
That's excellent.

144
00:09:34,560 --> 00:09:36,070
I'll go to the palace right away

145
00:09:36,070 --> 00:09:37,890
to recommend Xiao Yehan
for the relief work.

146
00:09:38,990 --> 00:09:41,360
Liu Chun, the medical official in Jiangzhou,
is one of my people.

147
00:09:41,800 --> 00:09:43,400
If Xiao Yehan takes on the relief work,

148
00:09:43,840 --> 00:09:46,190
at best, he will likely fail

149
00:09:46,190 --> 00:09:47,280
and be heavily impeached.

150
00:09:47,720 --> 00:09:49,110
At worst, he could contract the plague

151
00:09:49,110 --> 00:09:50,360
and never return.

152
00:09:57,150 --> 00:09:58,050
Your Highness,

153
00:09:58,880 --> 00:10:00,730
do you have to go to Jiangzhou?

154
00:10:01,480 --> 00:10:02,480
Speak your mind.

155
00:10:04,430 --> 00:10:06,960
This relief mission was strongly
recommended by Prince Yan.

156
00:10:06,960 --> 00:10:09,070
Last time, he didn't succeed
in the assassination.

157
00:10:09,070 --> 00:10:11,690
I'm just worried
that this might be a trap.

158
00:10:12,760 --> 00:10:15,240
The people of Jiangzhou
are suffering greatly.

159
00:10:15,640 --> 00:10:17,280
How can I sit back and do nothing?

160
00:10:17,990 --> 00:10:19,810
Even if there are dangers ahead,

161
00:10:19,990 --> 00:10:21,480
I have to go.

162
00:10:23,680 --> 00:10:24,570
However,

163
00:10:24,840 --> 00:10:25,850
before that,

164
00:10:26,640 --> 00:10:28,280
I need to go somewhere first.

165
